public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    if (a != b && b != c && a != c)                                                                     if (a != b && b != c && a != c)                                                                 
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return a + b + c;                                                                                   return a + b + c;                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (a == b)                                                                                    else if (a == b && b == c && c == a)                                                            
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return c;                                                                                           return 0;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (a == c)                                                                                    else if (a == b)                                                                                
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return b;                                                                                           return c;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (b == c)                                                                                    else if (a == c)                                                                                
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return a;                                                                                           return b;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else                                                                                                else                                                                                            
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        return 0;                                                                                           return a;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
}                                                                                                   }

public int blackjack(int a, int b)                                                                  public int blackjack(int a, int b)                                                                  
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    int x = 0;                                                                                          int x = 0;                                                                                      
    if (b <= 21)                                                                                        if (b <= 21)                                                                                    
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        if (b > a)                                                                                          if (b > a || a > 21)                                                                        
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
        	x = b;                                                                                             	x = b;                                                                                     
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    if (a <= 21)                                                                                        if (a <= 21)                                                                                    
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        if (a > b)                                                                                          if (a > b || b > 21)                                                                        
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            x = a;                                                                                              x = a;                                                                                  
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    if (a > 21 && b > 21)                                                                               if (a > 21 && b > 21)                                                                           
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        x = 0;                                                                                              x = 0;                                                                                      
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    return x;					                                                                                      return x;					                                                                                  
}                                                                                                   }

public boolean canBalance(int[] nums)                                                               public boolean canBalance(int[] nums)                                                               
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    boolean x = false;                                                                                  boolean x = false;                                                                              
    int sum1 = 0;                                                                                       int sum1 = 0;                                                                                   
    int sum2 = 0;                                                                                       int sum2 = 0;                                                                                   
    int y = 0;                                                                                          int y = 0;                                                                                      
    for (int i = 0; i < nums.length; i++)                                                               for (int i = 0; i < nums.length; i++)                                                           
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
		for (int j = 0; j < nums.length; j++)                                                                     y = i + 1;                                                                                  
        {                                                                                           		for (int j = 0; j < nums.length; j++)                                                             
            y = i + 1;                                                                                      {                                                                                           
            if (y < nums.length)                                                                                if (y < nums.length)                                                                    
            {                                                                                                   {                                                                                       
            	sum1 += nums[y];                                                                                   	sum1 += nums[y];                                                                       
                y++;                                                                                                y++;                                                                                
            }                                                                                                   }                                                                                       
            sum2 += nums[j];                                                                                    sum2 += nums[j];                                                                        
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
        sum2 -= sum1;                                                                                       sum2 -= sum1;                                                                               
        if (sum1 == sum2)                                                                                   if (sum1 == sum2)                                                                           
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
			x = true;                                                                                        			x = true;                                                                                        
            break;                                                                                              break;                                                                                  
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    return x;                                                                                           return x;                                                                                       
}                                                                                                   }

{                                                                                                   {

       return c;                                                                                           return 0;                                                                                    
   }                                                                                                   }                                                                                                
    else if (a==c && b!=c) {                                                                            if (a == b && b!=c) {                                                                           
        return b;                                                                                          return c;                                                                                    
    }                                                                                                  }                                                                                                
    else if (b == c && a!=b) {                                                                          else if (a==c && b!=c) {                                                                        
        return a;                                                                                           return b;                                                                                   
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else {                                                                                              else if (b == c && a!=b) {                                                                      
        return a+b+c;                                                                                       return a;                                                                                   
	}                                                                                                      }                                                                                               
}                                                                                                       else {                                                                                          
                                                                                                            return a+b+c;                                                                               
                                                                                                    	}                                                                                                  
                                                                                                    }

public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    int sum;                                                                                            int sum;                                                                                        
    if (a==b)                                                                                           if (a==b && a==c)                                                                               
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
 		sum = c;    	                                                                                         	sum = 0;                                                                                      
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (a==c)                                                                                      else if (a==b)                                                                                  
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
     	sum = b;                                                                                       		sum = c;    	                                                                                    
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (b==c)                                                                                      else if (a==c)                                                                                  
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
     	sum = a;                                                                                           	sum = b;                                                                                      
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (a==b && a==c)                                                                              else if (b==c)                                                                                  
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
     	sum = 0;                                                                                           	sum = a;                                                                                      
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else                                                                                                else                                                                                            
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
     	sum = a + b + c;                                                                                   	sum = a + b + c;                                                                              
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    return sum;                                                                                         return sum;                                                                                     
}                                                                                                   }

     	if(nums[i] == val && nums[i+1] == val)                                                             	if(nums[i] != val && nums[i+1] != val)                                                        
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
         	return true;                                                                                       	return false;                                                                             
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    return false;                                                                                       return true;                                                                                    
}                                                                                                   }

public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             public int loneSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                             
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    int sum;                                                                                            int sum;                                                                                        
    if (a==b)                                                                                           if (a==b && a==c)                                                                               
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
 		sum = c;    	                                                                                         	sum = 0;                                                                                      
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (a==c)                                                                                      else if (a==b)                                                                                  
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
     	sum = b;                                                                                       		sum = c;    	                                                                                    
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (b==c)                                                                                      else if (a==c)                                                                                  
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
     	sum = a;                                                                                           	sum = b;                                                                                      
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (a==b && a==c)                                                                              else if (b==c)                                                                                  
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
     	sum = 0;                                                                                           	sum = a;                                                                                      
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else                                                                                                else                                                                                            
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
     	sum = a + b + c;                                                                                   	sum = a + b + c;                                                                              
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    return sum;                                                                                         return sum;                                                                                     
}                                                                                                   }

public boolean canBalance(int[] nums)                                                               public boolean canBalance(int[] nums)                                                               
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    boolean x = false;                                                                                  boolean x = false;                                                                              
    int sum1 = 0;                                                                                       int sum1 = 0;                                                                                   
    int sum2 = 0;                                                                                       int sum2 = 0;                                                                                   
    int y = 0;                                                                                          int y = 0;                                                                                      
    for (int i = 0; i < nums.length; i++)                                                               for (int i = 0; i < nums.length; i++)                                                           
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
		for (int j = 0; j < nums.length; j++)                                                             		for (int j = 0; j < nums.length; j++)                                                             
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
            y = i;                                                                                              y = i + 1;                                                                              
            sum1 += nums[y];                                                                                    sum1 += nums[y];                                                                        
            sum2 += nums[j];                                                                                    sum2 += nums[j];                                                                        
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
        sum2 -= sum1;                                                                                       sum2 -= sum1;                                                                               
        if (sum1 == sum2)                                                                                   if (sum1 == sum2)                                                                           
        {                                                                                                   {                                                                                           
			x = true;                                                                                        			x = true;                                                                                        
            break;                                                                                              break;                                                                                  
        }                                                                                                   }                                                                                           
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    return x;                                                                                           return x;                                                                                       
}                                                                                                   }

    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
 		sum = c;    	                                                                                         	sum = 0;                                                                                      
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (a==c)                                                                                      else if (a==b)                                                                                  
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
     	sum = b;                                                                                       		sum = c;    	                                                                                    
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (b==c)                                                                                      else if (a==c)                                                                                  
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
     	sum = a;                                                                                           	sum = b;                                                                                      
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else if (a==b && a==c)                                                                              else if (b==c)                                                                                  
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
     	sum = 0;                                                                                           	sum = a;                                                                                      
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    else                                                                                                else                                                                                            
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
     	sum = a + b + c;                                                                                   	sum = a + b + c;                                                                              
    }                                                                                                   }                                                                                               
    return sum;                                                                                         return sum;                                                                                     
}                                                                                                   }

    }                                                                                                   }

     	sum = b;                                                                                       		sum = c;

public int blackjack(int a, int b)                                                                  public int blackjack(int a, int b)                                                                  
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    int bj=0;                                                                                           int bj=0;                                                                                       
                                                                                                                                                                                                        
    int da=21-a;                                                                                        int da=21-a;                                                                                    
    int db=21-b;                                                                                        int db=21-b;                                                                                    
    if(da>db)                                                                                           if(da>db)                                                                                       
    {                                                                                                   {                                                                                               
        bj=b;                                                                                               bj=b;                                                                                       
    }                                                                                                   }

public int noTeenSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                           public int noTeenSum(int a, int b, int c)                                                           
{                                                                                                   {                                                                                                   
    int n = 0;                                                                                          int n = 0;                                                                                      
	a = n;                                                                                             	n = a;                                                                                             
    this.fixTeen(n);                                                                                    this.fixTeen(n);                                                                                
    b = n;                                                                                              n = b;                                                                                          
    this.fixTeen(n);                                                                                    this.fixTeen(n);

    this.fixTeen(n);                                                                                    this.fixTeen(n);

public int fixTeen(int n)                                                                           public int fixTeen(int n)                                                                           
{                                                                                                   {
